roup 的各种 IP 相关商品的开发。开幕前活动将在正式开幕前开始。</p><p>单击此处获取每个站点的链接。<br />・ 试镜网站：https: <a href="https://globie.net/audition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">//globie.net/audition</a><br />・FavieBox 网站： <a href="https://faviebox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://faviebox.com/</a> </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="card shadow overflow-hidden"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/06/202306012028918000.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal">勇者集团拓展海外英语VTuber项目“V4Mirai”第一批登场！</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2"> Brave group, Inc.宣布在美国旧金山成立“Brave group US Inc.”。来自新的 VTuber 项目“V4Mirai”的两名 VTuber，专门研究英语 [...]</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2023.06.02</span></div></div></div></div><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000203.000044525.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻稿</a></p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/brave-group-europe/">Brave 集团成立“Brave 集团欧洲” 推出欧洲多语言 VTuber 项目</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
